one_Shards\" title=\"Bone Shards\"><img alt=\"Bone Shards.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bone_Shards.png?291c61\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Living_Log\" title=\"Living Log\"><img alt=\"Living Log.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Living_Log.png?bdc25f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bramble_Husk\" title=\"Bramble Husk\"><img alt=\"Bramble Husk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bramble_Husk.png?f49297\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wormwood\" title=\"Wormwood\"><img alt=\"Wormwood Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wormwood_Portrait.png/64px-Wormwood_Portrait.png?d47f44\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Bone Shards were first introduced in the <i>Reign of Giants</i> DLC. In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve/Version_History\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve/Version History\">Quality of Life</a></i> update, they were retroactively added to the base game.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:A_Little_Rain_Must_Fall.jpg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Bone Shards as seen in the poster for A Little Rain Must Fall update.\"><img alt=\"Bone Shards as seen in the poster for A Little Rain Must Fall update.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/A_Little_Rain_Must_Fall.jpg/65px-A_Little_Rain_Must_Fall.jpg?ed7ed3\" width=\"65\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Bone Shards as seen in the poster for <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve/Version_History#March_12,_2013_-_A_Little_Rain_Must_Fall\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve/Version History\">A Little Rain Must Fall</a></i> update.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
